meta {
  name: GET all partners — see createdBy values
  type: http
  seq: 4
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/odata/v4/orders/BusinessPartners
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
}

docs {
  ## req.user demo — step 4

  Read all partners to see the `createdBy` field stamped by the server.

  After running steps 1 and 3:
  - Lockheed → createdBy: "alice"
  - Shopify   → createdBy: "bob"

  The client never sent `createdBy` — the server stamped it from req.user.id.
}
